# EpubFileReadInTest : ReadMe

This is a Epub file analyzing application for Universal Windows Platform. The minimum supported SDK is windows10 1809. 

The EpubUnzip class is a pakage for epub format file read in and serialize components into Objects in C#(.NET). And it's basic funtions were originally written during 2017 when I was tring to build an epub reading application for Windows phone but found no available epub libraries for .Net and UWP. 

I have finished a Webview  based version of the app but since Microsoft put forward fluent design system and provide more UI component for UWP. And Windows phone dies soon. So I try to restart the project based on new UI components. The current version only supports reading basic infomation of a epub file and reveal in the view.

More features and functions would be added to the application. And the EpubUnzip module would be improved.
